title: NOAA, Hurricane tracks in September, Global, 2006
name: NOAA, Hurricane tracks in September, Global, 2006
description:
The map is base on hurricane tracks extracted for the month of September from the NOAA's Hurricane website.
Hurricanes start as a low pressure disturbance off West-African cost. Some have theorized the seeding of a hurricane starts as a low pressure disturbance over Ethiopia.
